   "source": [
    "# 📊 Ethiopian Tech Salary Data - Comprehensive Exploration & Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "## Overview\n",
    "This notebook provides an in-depth exploration and analysis of Ethiopian technology sector salary data. We'll examine patterns, distributions, correlations, and insights that drive compensation in Ethiopia's growing tech industry.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Objectives:\n",
    "- 🔍 **Exploratory Data Analysis**: Understand data structure and quality\n",
    "- 📈 **Statistical Analysis**: Identify key patterns and distributions\n",
    "- 🎯 **Feature Analysis**: Examine relationships between variables\n",
    "- 🌍 **Geographic Insights**: Analyze location-based salary variations\n",
    "- 🎓 **Education Impact**: Study education level effects on compensation\n",
    "- 💼 **Department Analysis**: Compare salaries across tech departments\n",
    "\n",
    "---"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 📚 Import Libraries and Setup\n",
    "\n",
    "We'll use a comprehensive set of libraries for data analysis, visualization, and statistical testing."
